{"tid":2076734,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"與何君堯關係匪淺 前區議員林悅涉無牌經營移民公司","createTime":"2020-06-23T18:25:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T08:51:05.000Z","uid":240362,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"f35d0f78dbdd5e637182ee25f7a70a1f3f1461f3","tid":2076734,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T18:25:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200624/KPLGE34B4BAF6CQ353JZQ7WQMA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200624%2FKPLGE34B4BAF6CQ353JZQ7WQMA%2F&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4Jf3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=87cf4fd5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200624%2FKPLGE34B4BAF6CQ353JZQ7WQMA%2F&h=4c214b19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200624/KPLGE34B4BAF6CQ353JZQ7WQMA/</a><br />\n<br />\n一連串反修例運動，加上多個惡法煞港，黯淡未來令港人移民詢問度升溫，台灣是熱門之選。不過，苦主賴小姐向《蘋果》爆料，指與立法會議員何君堯關係匪淺、曾因詐騙被判監21個月的離島區東涌中區前區議員林悅，近年用洋名「Jeff Lam」轉型做移民KOL發圍，經營的Facebook專頁「台遊達人」有逾6萬粉絲，但涉嫌「重操故業」。賴小姐指，至少有7個家庭錯信林悅，交付金錢代辦移民，選用他提供的投資移民方案後，到期收不到應有回報，個案涉及最高金額達400萬元新台幣（下同，約104萬港元），她更說：「香港依家水深火熱，好多想移民的港人如盲頭烏蠅，我唔想再有香港人墮入陷阱。」"},{"pid":"00c7afabb5f6f14e5b927b4f6e819fd48bffdcd7","tid":2076734,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T18:27:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b468c4bc225fcadf37e8849971c4c999abf8653","tid":2076734,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T18:39:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd95410587193dd32f9c202be2f263aabf306075","tid":2076734,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T18:52:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"45f1bf9603364d143ab1485802348ee6bc9ad43c","